title: FormDesigner
shortDescription: Online designer of web forms, surveys, quizzes and calculato
longDescription:
FormDesigner.pro is a builder which allows you to create surveys, quizzes, tests, calculators, online record forms and any other web forms, without the help of a designer or programmer.

FormDesigner.pro is a great solution for creating both simple and very complex forms. Its unlimited possibilities allow you to create almost any form and customize it the way you want.

**Why use FormDesigner:**

* 90 ready-made templates on various themes
* Flexible settings
* Drag&Drop interface
* Advanced design settings
* Over 30 different question types
* Multiple questions on one page
* Auto save form data  
* Online recording feature with date and time locking in the calendar
* Ability to create reactive and personalized forms
* Logical rules and branching of questions and pages
* Smart redirects
* Print templates with form results
* Protection against bots and spoofing
* Integration with Analytics Systems
* Binding your domain
* Forms CNC Setting
* Suitable for any website
* There is a plugin for Wordpress
* Adaptability. Forms work great on both PCs and mobile devices
* Different ways to place the form: by direct link, in the body of the page, as a popup window, etc.
* 71k satisfied customers worldwide
* And more

To get acquainted with the service there is a free rate and a test period of 7 days.
author: Ivan Shamshur
